ion\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/defence.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">National security and defence</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/culture.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Culture, history and sport</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/policing.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Policing, justice and emergencies</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/transport.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Transport and infrastructure</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.international.gc.ca/world-monde/index.aspx?lang=eng\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Canada and the world</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/finance.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Money and finances</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/science.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Science and innovation</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/life-events.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Manage life events</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<nav id=\"wb-bc\" property=\"breadcrumb\"><h2 class=\"wb-inv\">You are here:</h2><div class=\"container\"><ol class=\"breadcrumb\">\n<li><a href=\"/en.html\">Canada.ca</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada.html\">Study in Canada as an international student</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit.html\">Study permit</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot.html\">Francophone Minority Communities Student Pilot</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/eligibility.html\">Who can apply</a></li>\n</ol></div></nav>\n</header>\n</div>\n</div>\n<main class=\"container\" property=\"mainContentOfPage\" resource=\"#wb-main\" typeof=\"WebPageElement\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<nav class=\"provisional gc-subway\">\n<h1 id=\"gc-document-nav\">Francophone Minority Communities Student Pilot</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/eligibility.html\">Who can apply</a> <a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/eligibility.html#gc-document-nav\">Who can apply</a></li>\n<li><a aria-current=\"page\" class=\"active\" href=\"#\">Participating designated learning institutions  and financial requirement</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/get-documents.html\">Get the right  documents</a> <a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/get-documents.html#gc-document-nav\">Get the right  documents</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/apply.html\">How to apply</a> <a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/apply.html#gc-document-nav\">How to apply</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/after-apply.html\">After you apply</a> <a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/after-apply.html#gc-document-nav\">After you apply</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/path-to-pr.html\">Path to permanent residence</a> <a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot/path-to-pr.html#gc-document-nav\">Path to permanent residence</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n<h1 id=\"wb-cont\" property=\"name\">Participating designated learning institutions and financial requirements</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h2>On this page</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#participating-dlis\">Participating DLIs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#how-much-money-you-need\">How much money you need to participate in the Francophone Minority Communities Student Pilot (FMCSP) </a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>To be eligible for a study permit under this pilot, you must</p>\n<ul>\n<li>apply to a program of study and receive a letter of acceptance from one of the <a href=\"#participating-dlis\">schools on the list below</a>\n<ul>\n<li>Make sure the school knows that you’re interested in applying for a study permit through the FMCSP.</li>\n<li>More participating schools may be added to the list below in the future.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>meet the financial requirement, which depends on the city where the main campus of your school is located\n    <ul>\n<li>This means you must have the <a href=\"#how-much-money-you-need\">amount of money listed below</a>, in addition to your first year of tuition and travel costs.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h2 id=\"participating-dlis\">Participating designated learning institutions </h2>\n<p>As agreements are reached with learning institutions (outside Quebec) to participate in the pilot, they will be added there. Please check the list regularly.</p>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<table class=\"wb-tables table table-striped table-condensed small\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>DLI name</th>\n<th>DLI number</th>\n<th>Campus(es)</th>\n<th>Province</th>\n<th>Earliest eligible semester</th>\n<th>Funds required</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://ustboniface.ca/etudiants-dans-les-communautes-francophones-en-situation-minoritaire\" rel=\"external\">Université de Saint-Boniface</a> (website available in French only)</td>\n<td>O19126670302</td>\n<td>Winnipeg</td>\n<td>Manitoba</td>\n<td>September 2026</td>\n<td>Group A</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.collegedelile.ca/?lang=en-US\" rel=\"external\">Collège de l’Île</a></td>\n<td>O19220114112</td>\n<td><details>\n<summary>Multiple campuses</summary>\n<p>Wellington, Deblois, Charlottetown</p>\n</details></td>\n<td>Prince Edward Island</td>\n<td>September 2025</td>\n<td>Group E</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://ustpaul.ca/en/international/francophone-minority-communities-student-pilot-fmcsp/\" rel=\"external\">Université Saint Paul</a></td>\n<td>O19395164265</td>\n<td>Ottawa</td>\n<td>Ontario</td>\n<td>September 2025</td>\n<td>Group A</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.uregina.ca/academics/programs/education/baccalaureat-education-francaise-elementaire-apres-diplome.html\" rel=\"external\">University of Regina</a></td>\n<td>O19425660270</td>\n<td>Regina</td>\n<td>Saskatchewan</td>\n<td>September 2025</td>\n<td>Group B</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://educacentre.com/formation-collegiale/programme-pilote-pour-les-etudiants-dans-les-communautes-francophones-en-situation-minoritaire/\" rel=\"external\">Collège Éducacentre</a> (website available in French only)</td>\n<td>O19832975987</td>\n<td>Surrey</td>\n<td>British Columbia</td>\n<td>September 2025</td>\n<td>Group A</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.usainteanne.ca/futurs-etudiants/etudiants-internationaux/avant-de-venir-au-canada/ppecfsm\" rel=\"external\">Université Saint-Anne</a> (website available in French only)</td>\n<td>O19391556726</td>\n<td>Church Point</td>\n<td>Nova Scotia</td>\n<td>January 2026</td>\n<td>Group E</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.uottawa.ca/study/francophone-minority-student-pilot-fmcsp\" rel=\"external\">University of Ottawa</a></td>\n<td>O19397188593</td>\n<td>Ottawa</td>\n<td>Ontario</td>\n<td>September 2025</td>\n<td>Group A</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://laurentian.ca/\" rel=\"external\">Université Laurentienne</a> (website available in French only)</td>\n<td>O19304259382</td>\n<td>Sudbury</td>\n<td>Ontario</td>\n<td>September 2025</td>\n<td>Group B</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://uofinternational.ca/en/\" rel=\"external\">Université de l’Ontario français</a></td>\n<td>O146030735072</td>\n<td>Toronto</td>\n<td>Ontario</td>\n<td>September 2025</td>\n<td>Group A</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.yorku.ca/glendon/francophone-community-minorities-student-pilot-fmcsp/\" rel=\"external\">York University</a></td>\n<td>O19361109242</td>\n<td>Glendon (Toronto)</td>\n<td>Ontario</td>\n<td>September 2025</td>\n<td>Group A</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://uhearst.ca/demande-ppecfsm/\" rel=\"external\">Université de Hearst</a> (website available in French only)</td>\n<td>O19395677925</td>\n<td><details>\n<summary>Multiple campuses</summary>\n<p>Hearst, Kapuskasing, Timmins</p>\n</details></td>\n<td>Ontario</td>\n<td>September 2025</td>\n<td>Group E</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.ualberta.ca/en/campus-saint-jean/programs/international/index.html\" rel=\"external\">University of Alberta</a></td>\n<td>O19257171832</td>\n<td>Edmonton</td>\n<td>Alberta</td>\n<td>September 2025</td>\n<td>Group A</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://ccnb.ca/admission-et-inscription/etudiants-internationaux/\" rel=\"external\"