ol is located. You must also show that you have enough money to pay your tuition fees.</p>\n<details>\n<summary>If you apply on or after September 1, 2025</summary>\n<details>\n<summary id=\"group-a-after\">\n<h3 class=\"h4\">Group A - Population of 500,000 and over</h3>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<table class=\"table table-hover\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"bg-primary\">\n<th>Number of family members (including the applicant) </th>\n<th>Amount of funds required per year (not including tuition)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>CAN$22,895</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>CAN$28,502</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>CAN$35,040</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>CAN$42,543</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>CAN$48,252</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>CAN$54,420</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>CAN$60,589</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>If more than 7 people, each additional family member</td>\n<td>CAN$6,170</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary id=\"group-b-after\">\n<h3 class=\"h4\">Group B – Population of 100,000 to 499,999</h3>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<table class=\"table table-hover\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"bg-primary\">\n<th>Number of family members (including the applicant) </th>\n<th>Amount of funds required per year (not including tuition)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>CAN$19,718</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>CAN$24,546</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>CAN$30,176</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>CAN$36,638</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>CAN$41,553</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>CAN$46,866</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>CAN$52,178</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>If more than 7 people, each additional family member</td>\n<td>CAN$5,312</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary id=\"group-c-after\">\n<h3 class=\"h4\">Group C – Population of 30,000 to 99,999</h3>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\